# Cloudflare Pages redirects
#
# The short-URL aliases (/security.txt, /change-password, /sitemap.xml,
# /sitemap-0.xml, /spec/index) that used to live here are now served from
# functions/_middleware.ts instead, so each 301 can carry a Redirect-By
# header naming what performed the redirect. Pages' _redirects file cannot set
# custom response headers; the middleware can. See
# /spec/resilience/redirect-by/. Keep this file for any future header-less
# redirects.
